ChangeList.Description: Added new delegated permissions [AppCatalog.Read.All](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#appcatalog-resource-permissions), [ChatMessage.Send](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#chatmessage-permissions), [Teams.Create](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#teams-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadForUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadWriteForUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadWriteSelfForUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions).

Added new application permissions [Teams.Create](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#teams-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadForUser.All](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadWriteForUser.All](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions), [TeamsAppInstallation.ReadWriteSelfForUser.All](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#Teams-app-installation-permissions).
Added the **azureADAppId** property to [teamsAppDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamsAppDefinition?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added permissions for [resource-specific consent](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/permissions-reference#teams-resource-specific-consent-permissions).
Added support for sending [channel messages](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chatmessage?view=graph-rest-1.0) and channel message replies.
Added support for getting the **filesFolder** of a [channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/channel?view=graph-rest-1.0).

Introduced the Shifts APIs, including [shift](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/shift?view=graph-rest-1.0), [workforceintegration](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/workforceintegration?view=graph-rest-1.0), and associated methods.
Added new property **supportedEntities** to [workforceintegration](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/workforceintegration?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added support for ChannelMessage.Read.All to APIs for reading [chatMessages](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chatmessage?view=graph-rest-beta) in channels.
Added new entity [teamwork](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamwork?view=graph-rest-1.0).
Added [notifications](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/subscription-post-subscriptions?view=graph-rest-beta) for all channel messages in tenant and all chat messages in tenant.
Added the [swapShiftsChangeRequest: decline](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/swapshiftschangerequest-decline?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the **swapShiftsChangeRequest** resource.
Added **primaryChannel** navigation property to team resource type.
Added [notifications](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/subscription-post-subscriptions?view=graph-rest-beta) for new and edited channel messages, and new and edited chat messages.
Added the [shiftpreferences](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/shiftpreferences?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and associated methods.
Added new relationship **shiftPreferences** to [userSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/usersettings?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.

Updated the application permissions required to perform read and write operations for shifts resources, including [schedule](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/schedule?view=graph-rest-beta), [schedulingGroup](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/schedulinggroup?view=graph-rest-beta), [shift](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/shift?view=graph-rest-beta), [timeOff](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/timeoff?view=graph-rest-beta), [timeOffReason](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/timeoffreason?view=graph-rest-beta), [timeOffRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/timeoffrequest?view=graph-rest-beta), [swapShiftChangeRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/swapshiftchangerequest?view=graph-rest-beta), and [openShiftChangeRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/openshiftchangerequest?view=graph-rest-beta). **Note:** Applications permissions are currently in private preview and are not available for public use.

Added the [openshift](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/openshift?view=graph-rest-beta), [openshiftChangeRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/openshiftChangeRequest?view=graph-rest-beta), [swapShiftChangeRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/swapShiftChangeRequest?view=graph-rest-beta), and [timeoffrequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/timeoffrequest?view=graph-rest-beta) resources and associated methods.

Added the **timeClockEnabled**, **openShiftsEnabled**, **swapShiftsRequestsEnabled**, **offerShiftRequestsEnabled**,  **timeOffRequestsEnabled** properties to the [schedule](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/schedule?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added an additional route to retrieve a [driveItem] using a team and channel ID, [get driveItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/driveitem-get?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the [Get team photo](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/team-get-photo?view=graph-rest-beta) and [Update team photo](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/team-update-photo?view=graph-rest-beta) methods.
[Reading images in messages](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/chatmessagehostedcontent-get?view=graph-rest-beta) now support application permissions.
Added the **primaryChannel** property to the [team](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/team?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **allowCreatePrivateChannels** property to the [teamMemberSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teammembersettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the ability to pull incremental messages from channels with the [channel messages delta query API](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-messages-delta?view=graph-rest-beta).

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: add members to a private channel
ChangeList.Description: Added the ability to [add members to a private channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/conversationmember-add?view=graph-rest-beta).
ChangeList.Target: add members to a private channel

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: remove members from a private channel
ChangeList.Description: Added the ability to [remove members from a private channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/conversationmember-delete?view=graph-rest-beta).
ChangeList.Target: remove members from a private channel

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: update a member's role in a private channel
ChangeList.Description: Added the ability to [update a member's role in a private channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/conversationmember-update?view=graph-rest-beta).
ChangeList.Target: update a member's role in a private channel

ChangeList.Description: Added the **membershipType** property to the [channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/channel?view=graph-rest-beta) resource to show if a particular channel is private or standard.

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: List channel messages,Get channel message,List replies to a message,Get a reply to a message
ChangeList.Description: Added support for application permissions to [List channel messages](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-list-messages?view=graph-rest-beta), [Get channel message](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-get-message?view=graph-rest-beta), [List replies to a message](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-list-messagereplies?view=graph-rest-beta), and [Get a reply to a message](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-get-messagereply?view=graph-rest-beta).
ChangeList.Target: List channel messages,Get channel message,List replies to a message,Get a reply to a message

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: List messages in a chat,Get message in chat
ChangeList.Description: Added support for application permissions to [List messages in a chat](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/chatmessage-list?view=graph-rest-beta) and [Get message in chat](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/chatmessage-get?view=graph-rest-beta).
ChangeList.Target: List messages in a chat,Get message in chat

ChangeList.Description: Added the **installedApps** property to the [chat](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chat?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added navigation binding for **chats** property of the [user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [teamwork](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [userTeamwork](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/userteamwork?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: user,List apps installed for user,Install app for user,Uninstall app for user,Upgrade app installed for user
ChangeList.Description:
Added new methods to the [user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource enabling the following methods with personal apps for users:
[List apps installed for user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/user-list-teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-beta)
[Install app for user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/user-add-teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-beta)
[Uninstall app for user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/user-delete-teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-beta)
[Upgrade app installed for user](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/user-upgrade-teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-beta)
ChangeList.Target: user,List apps installed for user,Install app for user,Uninstall app for user,Upgrade app installed for user

ChangeList.Description: Added the [teamDiscoverySettings](/api-reference/beta/resources/teamdiscoverysettings.md) resource and associated methods.
Added **urgent** property to the **chatMessageImportance** enum.
Added **hostedContents** navigation property to the [chatMessage](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chatmessage?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.

Added **chatMessageHostedContent** entity to represent content hosted by Microsoft Teams associated with a [chatMessage](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chatmessage?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added the [chat](/api-reference/beta/resources/chat.md) resources and associated methods.
Added APIs to read [images](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/chatmessagehostedimage?view=graph-rest-beta) in messages.
Added the [conversation member](/api-reference/beta/resources/conversationmember.md) resources and associated methods.
Added support for application permissions to the [installedApps](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **email** and **webUrl** properties to [channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/channel?view=graph-rest-1.0).

Added the [schedule](/api-reference/beta/resources/schedule.md), [schedulingGroup](/api-reference/beta/resources/schedulinggroup.md), [shift](/api-reference/beta/resources/shift.md), [timeOffReason](/api-reference/beta/resources/timeoffreason.md) and [timeOff](/api-reference/beta/resources/timeoff.md) resources and associated methods.

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: Send a message to a channel
ChangeList.Description: Introduced the [Send a message to a channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-post-messages?view=graph-rest-beta) API.
ChangeList.Target: Send a message to a channel

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: Reply to a message in a channel
ChangeList.Description: Introduced the [Reply to a message in a channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-post-messagereply?view=graph-rest-beta) API.
ChangeList.Target: Reply to a message in a channel

ChangeList.ChangedApiName: Create a message in a channel
ChangeList.Description: Removed the POST /teams/{id}/channels/{id}/chatThreads API. Use [Create a message in a channel](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/channel-post-chatmessage?view=graph-rest-beta) instead.
ChangeList.Target: Create a message in a channel

ChangeList.Description: Added support for application permissions to the [installedApps](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamsappinstallation?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **internalId** property to the [team](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/team?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added support for configuring Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDF, and document library [tabs](teams-configuring-builtin-tabs.md).

Added educationStandard, educationClass, educationProfessionalLearningCommunity, educationStaff, and unknownFutureValue to the [teamSpecialization](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/teamspecialization?view=graph-rest-beta) enum.
